Descriptions.Text:
Bring doom upon the enemy, dealing {1} Shadow damage and bursting up to {2} Festering Wounds on the target.

Summons an Army of the Dead ghoul for {3} sec for each burst Festering Wound.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {4} Runes.}

Deals {1} Shadow damage and infects all enemies within {2} yds with Blood Plague.

|Tinterface\icons\spell_deathknight_bloodplague.blp:24|t {FFFFFFFF|Blood Plague}
A shadowy disease that drains {3} health from the target over {4} sec.

Reach out with necrotic tendrils, dealing {1} Shadow damage and applying Blood Plague to your target and generating {2} Bone Shield charges.

|Tinterface\icons\spell_deathknight_bloodplague.blp:24|t {FFFFFFFF|Blood Plague}
A shadowy disease that drains {3} health from the target over {4} sec.

Ваша [Безжальна Зима] та [Льодяні Окови] застосовують [Смертельний Холод], вкорінюючи ціль на місці протягом {1} секунди.

{FFFFFFFFF| Безжальна Зима} 
Усі цілі в межах {2} ярдів страждають від [Смертельного холоду], коли використовується [Безжальна Зима].

{FFFFFFFFF| Льодяні Окови}
Коли ви застосовуєту [Льодяні Окови] на мішень, яка вже постраждала від ваших [Льодяних Оков], вона будуть вражена [Смертельним Холодом].

Strikes for {1} Physical damage and infects the target with {2}-{3} Festering Wounds.

|Tinterface\icons\spell_yorsahj_bloodboil_purpleoil.blp:24|t {FFFFFFFF|Festering Wound}
A pustulent lesion that will burst on death or when damaged by Scourge Strike, dealing {4} Shadow damage and generating {5} Runic Power.

Smash the target, dealing {1} Physical damage and generating {2} charges of Bone Shield.

|Tinterface\icons\ability_deathknight_boneshield.blp:24|t {FFFFFFFF|Bone Shield}
Surrounds you with a barrier of whirling bones, increasing Armor by {3}. Each melee attack against you consumes a charge. Lasts {4} sec or until all charges are consumed.

The cooldown of your Apocalypse is reduced by {1} sec, but your Apocalypse no longer summons ghouls but instead applies Crypt Fever to the target.

{FFFFFFFF|Crypt Fever}
Deals up to {2}% of the targets maximum health in Shadow damage over {3} sec. Healing spells cast on this target will refresh the duration of Crypt Fever.

Deals {1} Shadow damage to the target and infects all nearby enemies with Virulent Plague.

|Tinterface\icons\ability_creature_disease_02.blp:24|t {FFFFFFFF|Virulent Plague}
A disease that deals {2} Shadow damage over {3} sec. It erupts when the infected target dies, dealing {4} Shadow damage to nearby enemies.

Summon a Gargoyle into the area to bombard the target for {1} sec.

The Gargoyle gains {2}% increased damage for every {3} Runic Power you spend.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {4} Runic Power.}
